Ogbomosho South bụ mpaghara Gọọmentị dị na Oyo Steeti, Naịjirịa
Isi ụlọ ọrụ ya dị na mpaghara Arowomole nke Ogbomosho.
O nwere mpaghara nke 88 km2 na ọnụ ọgụgụ mmadụ 185,815 dika ọnụ ọgụgụ afọ 2006 sị di.
Koodu ozi nke mpaghara ahụ bụ 210.
E guzobere Gọọmentị mpaghara Ogbomoso South na 1991 site na Gọọmentụ Obodo Oggomoso gara aga site n'aka ndị agha
Mpaghara ndị dị na Kansụl ahụ gụnyere Idi- igba, Gaa- Lagbedu, Kajola, Kowe, Oke- Ola, Adeoye, Onidewure, Molete, Arowomole, Sanuaje, Obandi, Ijeru, Ayegun, na Oke Alapata.
